==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tergiferous
<hw>Ter*gif"er*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>tergum</ets> the back + <ets>-ferous</ets>.]</ety> <def>Carrying or
bearing upon the back.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Tergiferous plants</b></col> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>,
<cd>plants which bear their seeds on the back of their leaves, as
ferns.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tergite</ent>⟦br⟧
